QuestData.Title: Return to the Present
QuestData.Description:
This timeline is dark and chaotic. The disruption here has been severe. I shall remain in this timeline a moment more to help sort out what remaining ripples may appear.
Return to Nozdormu. He will want to know of our success, even if it was less complete than we would like.
QuestData.LogDescription: Return to Nozdormu in the Present.
QuestData.RewardText: Your journey did not accomplish our goals, but it was a success nonetheless.
